{"TopicId":157802,"ForumId":148,"TopicTitle":"KSP Making History","CreatedByName":"UomoCapra","CreatedById":167737,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-17T00:18:25Z","PageNum":33,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Capt. Hunt","CreatedById":97860,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-08T17:43:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223049260\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157802\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221494260733\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105198\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RoverDude\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, RoverDude said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNon-Disclosure Agreement. \u00A0It means we can\u0027t talk about stuff, nor can we confirm or deny stuff.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHe\u0027d tell us but then he\u0027d have to\u00A0 kill us.\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"theJesuit","CreatedById":122369,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-08T20:33:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223049192\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157802\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221494258564\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022113764\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Foxster\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 hours ago, Foxster said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSince Squad announced new stuff to do and new bits to do it with, I have felt all warm and fuzzy about Squad.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn fact, I\u0027d like to have their babies. Is that likely to be available in a forthcoming DLC?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor baby generation there tends to be a necessity for localisation.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPeace.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Third_OfFive","CreatedById":142954,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-08T21:20:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy did I not hear about this until now\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerbolExplorer","CreatedById":177191,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-09T06:51:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhats the date for the lunch.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Foxster","CreatedById":113764,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-09T15:14:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223050192\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157802\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221494312688\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022177191\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KerbolExplorer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, KerbolExplorer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhats the date for the lunch.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI really can\u0027t make lunch until Friday.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTGI\u0027s OK for you?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Planetace","CreatedById":195406,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-09T15:32:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do missions actually work? Arnt those the ones that help teach