 summer?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust curious. If I\u0027m not allowed to ask this I understand.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-05-10T13:38:22Z\u0022 title=\u002205/10/2017 01:38  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMay 10, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Third_OfFive\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Just Jim","CreatedById":148725,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-10T13:52:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223051970\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157802\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221494423466\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022142954\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Third_OfFive\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 minutes ago, Third_OfFive said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf I may ask, what is the rough ETA until this is released? I know it\u0027s not set, but what\u0027s the estimate? 2 weeks? 2 months? End of the summer?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust curious. If I\u0027m not allowed to ask this I understand.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey won\u0027t say. When part of an update is tracking down and fixing bugs, they usually don\u0027t know themselves until the last minute.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TOMMY (JEB 2.0)","CreatedById":156081,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-11T13:58:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ndlc=bad mod=good do it as a update or mod not dlc never as a dlc\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klesh","CreatedById":110814,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-11T14:33:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223053063\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157802\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221494511113\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022156081\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TOMMY (JEB 2.0)\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n34 minutes ago, TOMMY (JEB 2.0) said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ndlc=bad mod=good\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat about console players that cant use mods? \u00A0Just leave them out of the additional content?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"0111narwhalz","CreatedById":110660,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-11T14:34:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223053063\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157802\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221494511113\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022156081\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TOMMY (JEB 2.0)\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n33 minutes ago, TOMMY (JEB 2.0) said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ndlc=bad mod=good\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s a very absolutist statement. What about the fact that\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Eeventually\u003C/em\u003E, everyone who\u0027s going to buy KSP, will buy KSP (or at least the influx from new purchases becomes insustainable)? What about the fact that SQUAD\u0027s employees are employees, not hobbyists, and so have to be paid by SQUAD? How about the Paradox model of DLC, whereby the DLC funds continued development of the game? Now, there is plenty of bad DLC out there ($40 for two new maps!), but there is also good DLC ($10 for practically an entirely new game).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRarely, if ever, can one say \u0022A is good\u0022 or \u0022B is bad\u0022 with certainty.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"/not/pol/","CreatedById":172548,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-11T14:58:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222988169\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157802\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221489754301\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022131978\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022genbrien\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 3/17/2017 at 8:38 AM, genbrien said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know right?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nit sucks to have a life and be forced to charged people for WORKS you\u0027re doing\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat a world we\u0027re living in.....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nalready payed 40 dollars for the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Foxster","CreatedById":113764,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-11T15:01:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223053211\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157802\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221494514714\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022172548\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022/not/pol/\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, /not/pol/ said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nalready payed 40 dollars for the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...and if you don\u0027t want to pay any more then no one is making you.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"/not/pol/","CreatedById":172548,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-11T15:03:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223053218\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157802\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221494514892\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022113764\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Foxster\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Foxster said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...and if you don\u0027t want to pay any more then no one is making you.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmostly just salty about the way they went about it. why just before august(?) of 2013 why not all of 2013. alot of people most likely bought it during Christmas so it seems like a [censored] move to impose that kind of deadline.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-05-11T15:03:49Z\u0022 title=\u002205/11/2017 03:03  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMay 11, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by /not/pol/\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Curveball Anders","CreatedById":107529,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-11T15:04:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223053151\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157802\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221494513266\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110660\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00220111narwhalz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n26 minutes ago, 0111narwhalz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRarely, if ever, can one say \u0022A is good\u0022 or \u0022B is bad\u0022 with certainty.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd when said with certainty is almost always wrong \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022Four legs good, two legs bad\u0022 -- \u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Animal_Farm\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EGeorge Orwell - Animal Farm\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"0111narwhalz","CreatedById":110660,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-11T15:11:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223053221\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157802\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221494515006\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022172548\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022/not/pol/\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, /not/pol/ said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmostly just salty about the way they went about it. why just before august(?) of 2013 why not all of 2013. alot of people most likely bought it during Christmas so it seems like a [censored] move to impose that kind of deadline.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe deadline (which was April 30)\u00A0was made in April 2013. SQUAD made a mistake with the way they wrote their EULA, and they realised this sometime earlier. They needed to scramble to prevent larger problems. If you signed that EULA, you\u0027re entitled to the expansion free of charge (as was made clear in said EULA). The agreements made after were written differently and exclude this clause. Besides, April is pretty far from the holidays. Not many (read: no) people I know buy stuff (or even think about buying stuff) for Christmas in spring. It was possibly the least related-to-holiday time they could\u0027ve picked.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-05-11T15:12:43Z\u0022 title=\u002205/11/2017 03:12  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMay 11, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by 0111narwhalz\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TOMMY (JEB 2.0)","CreatedById":156081,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-11T15:12:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223053147\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157802\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221494513219\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110814\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klesh\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n41 minutes ago, klesh said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat about console players that cant use mods? \u00A0Just leave them out of the additional content?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFine then make dlc free\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo it mod with consal compatability\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-05-11T15:15:19Z\u0022 title=\u002205/11/2017 03:15  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMay 11, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by TOMMY (JEB 2.0)\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"0111narwhalz","CreatedById":110660,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-11T15:15:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223053238\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157802\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221494515579\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022156081\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TOMMY (JEB 2.0)\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, TOMMY (JEB 2.0) said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFine then make dlc free\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are serious economic problems that would result from that. Namely, SQUAD would have little to no revenue and would be forced to either make a new game (abandoning KSP) or break up (abandoning KSP). Companies which give their products away for free are not long-lived companies.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSQUAD has to charge. You do not have to buy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-05-11T15:16:13Z\u0022 title=\u002205/11/2017 03:16  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMay 11, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by 0111narwhalz\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"/not/pol/","CreatedById":172548,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-11T15:17:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223053234\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157802\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221494515481\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110660\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00220111narwhalz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, 0111narwhalz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe deadline (which was April 30)\u00A0was made in April 2013. SQUAD made a mistake with the way they wrote their EULA, and they realised this sometime earlier. If you signed that EULA, you\u0027re entitled to the expansion free of charge (as was made clear in said EULA). The agreements made after were written differently and exclude this clause. Besides, \u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003EApril is pretty far from the holidays\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E. Not many (read: no) people I know buy stuff (or even think about buying stuff) for Christmas in spring. It was possibly the least related-to-holiday time they could\u0027ve picked.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI see why they made that decision but i still see it as a [Censored] move. although i do agree the deadline would be reasonable. but so early in 2013 is [REDACTED]\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-05-11T16:19:55Z\u0022 title=\u002205/11/2017 04:19  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMay 11, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Frybert\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"0111narwhalz","CreatedById":110660,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-11T15:20:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223053248\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157802\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221494515834\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022172548\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022/not/pol/\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, /not/pol/ said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI see why they made that decision but i still see it as a [Censored] move. although i do agree the deadline would be reasonable. but so early in 2013 is [REDACTED]\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo when would you suggest? Remember, KSP was starting to grow and SQUAD was losing future sales every time someone bought the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-05-11T16:21:22Z\u0022 title=\u002205/11/2017 04:21  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMay 11, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Frybert\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"/not/pol/","CreatedById":172548,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-11T15:22:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223053257\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157802\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221494516005\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110660\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00220111narwhalz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, 0111narwhalz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHeh.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo when would you suggest? Remember, KSP was starting to grow and SQUAD was losing future sales every time someone bought the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmost likely not under a month after it became available on steam.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}